snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Speed Freeks Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
A first look at Warhammer 40,000: SPEED FREEKS. A 16 player, Free-To-Play, multiplayer racing-shooter mayhem with Orks set in the badass Warhammer 40,000 universe – now available in Open Alpha!

#warhammer #warhammerskulls #gaming
